**发现 1**  
ID: `AR2-R2-01`  
Severity: `HIGH`  
Category: `Authorization`  
Type: `Bypass`  
Before-behavior: R1 中受限角色可直接请求 `ranking/top_bottom`。  
After-behavior: R2 只在请求体显式传入 `metrics` 时才做裁剪；若省略 `metrics`，`build_report()` 会回退到全量默认指标，受限角色仍可拿到 `ranking/top_bottom`。  
Evidence: [plan.md](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-05-analytics-report-plan.md#L1567), [plan.md](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-05-analytics-report-plan.md#L1571), [plan.md](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-05-analytics-report-plan.md#L972)  
Impact: `parent/homeroom_teacher/subject_teacher` 仍可越权获取敏感排名数据。  
Repair hypothesis: 路由层先计算 `allowed_metrics`；`metrics` 缺省时填充“允许的默认集合”，不要把 `None` 直接传给 `build_report()`；同样逻辑应复用到导出/AI 路径。  

**发现 2**  
ID: `AR2-R2-02`  
Severity: `HIGH`  
Category: `Authorization`  
Type: `Missing permission check`  
Before-behavior: 设计要求分数段配置接口受 `MANAGE_SCHOOL_SETTINGS` 保护。  
After-behavior: R2 的 `GET/PUT/DELETE /segments/config` 都只依赖 `get_current_user`，没有挂权限依赖。  
Evidence: [plan.md](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-05-analytics-report-plan.md#L727), [plan.md](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-05-analytics-report-plan.md#L750), [plan.md](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-05-analytics-report-plan.md#L775), [design.md](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-05-analytics-report-design.md#L57), [design.md](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-05-analytics-report-design.md#L58)  
Impact: 任意已登录角色都可能读取或篡改学校级分数段配置。  
Repair hypothesis: 三个路由统一改为 `Depends(require_permission(Permission.MANAGE_SCHOOL_SETTINGS))`。  

**发现 3**  
ID: `AR2-R2-03`  
Severity: `HIGH`  
Category: `Authorization`  
Type: `Incomplete fix`  
Before-behavior: R1 主要依赖 DataScope，趋势接口角色矩阵未显式落地。  
After-behavior: R2 只给 `class_trend` 做了班级集合校验、给 `student_trend` 做了学生可见性校验，但 `grade_trend` 没有任何角色门禁，`class_trend` 也未明确阻止家长角色。  
Evidence: [plan.md](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-05-analytics-report-plan.md#L1585), [plan.md](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-05-analytics-report-plan.md#L1601), [design.md](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-05-analytics-report-design.md#L170), [design.md](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-04-05-analytics-report-design.md#L176)  
Impact: 低权限角色仍可能访问不该暴露的年级/班级趋势聚合数据。  
Repair hypothesis: 在三个趋势路由前增加显式角色白名单/黑名单校验，不要只依赖 `visible_class_ids`。  

